title: Chapter 1807 - She Really Rises To The Occasion

Chapter 1807 - She Really Rises To The Occasion

Barrenwood Island.

A massive island in the far reaches of the Eastern Sea.

Churning waves surged over from afar, slamming the surrounding reef and spraying snow-white droplets. The sound was like the low rumble of thunder.

Numerous groups were clustered on the shore. The various camps were distributed throughout the area. 

Their ranks included numerous Immortal Kings of Jade Firmament Immortal Palace, Floating Mountain, and Penglai Immortal Island.

Them aside, there were members of the ancient races that made the Eastern Sea their home, like the Kui Ox and Ba Serpents. Even the weakest of these experts was an early-stage Immortal King.

It was no exaggeration to say that you could pick anyone here at random and find someone capable of shaking the Eastern Sea with a stomp of their foot.

But now, all of these prominent experts had withdrawn their auras, and all of them were perfectly polite. Rather, they drew no attention to themselves whatsoever.

This was because the true stars of the show, the ones who really drew attention, were the divine children whoâ€™d come here from the God Domain!
